seller.description:
Welcome to my profile! 
My name is Gleni and I lead a small team of Website Developers and SEO Experts, ready to be on your service. Here you will find the ideal service for those who require monthly technical support and also to integrate WordPress Plugins or Themes. We have more 15 years of combined experience in WordPress, SEO and more.

reviews.comment: I have some wordpress knowledge but I knew that I could never build a website for myself. I opted for gleniis as they seem to build nice looking websites over wordpress. I still have some work to do on my own but they helped me with most of the work by actually building all the pages, something I would never do by myself.

Gleni was fantastic. He heard my needs clearly, asked great questions and was able to deliver a fantastic product. I needed the website for my company's marketing and he got it to a point where it communicated the offerings very well. Gleni and his team are also good at creating visually attractive products. I gave him high level guidance on 'needs to be black, visually attractive, modern-looking' and he was able to deliver with those kind of keywords. If I have more additions to the website, I will be back!

Gleni and his team in the background are doing a great job. A short briefing is all it takes and Gleni and his team understand the customer's needs. 

The arrangements and updates during the project are also very professional. You get far more here than you pay for at first glance. I will book Gleni and his team again.

It was the right decision to commission Gleni. All agreements were adhered to and all change requests were implemented immediately. He absolutely fulfilled my expectations. I will hire him again next time. Delievery was even before the agreed deadline. Many thanks Gleni.

Gleniis exceeded my expectations in web development. He was attentive and committed to bringing my ideas to life. He tailored every aspect of the website precisely to my specifications, resulting in a site that surpassed my vision. He also handled domain setup seamlessly. His exceptional service, technical knowledge, and commitment to customer satisfaction make him worth every penny. If you’re seeking high-quality, customized web solutions with outstanding customer service, Gleniis is the best choice.
I thoroughly enjoy working with you repeatedly on your server and hosting needs. I look forward to collaborating with you on more projects in the future. You are excellent.
I had a great experience integrating with your WHMCS platform.
He's very polite person I really like to work with him :)
I am enjoying working with you.
